类 FutureMessage<M extends Message>

public class FutureMessage<M extends Message>
extends com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractFuture<Message>
Implementation of a Future for Messages that are being added to the Log via Log.add(org.janusgraph.diskstorage.StaticBuffer). This class can be used by Log implementations to wrap messages.
作者:
Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
